Created by: Adam K
Google+: http://gplus.to/smspopup
Blog: http://www.everythingandroid.net

SMS Popup provides a convenient popup dialog when a message is received that allows you to quickly read and reply to messages. It also provides in-depth customization of message notifications including contact specific sound, vibrate and LED settings.

Feel free to email me any comments, suggestions or bugs.

Credits to Min Tran for the app icon.

To avoid conflicts and multiple alerts, please disable the system SMS notifications and any other apps that provide a notification when a SMS is received.\n\nTo turn off the system notification, go to the messaging app, hit menu -> settings and un-check notifications.
Notifications for all contacts without an individual customization

SMS Popup offers the ability to customize notifications on a per contact basis. When a new message comes in, SMS Popup will first check if the contact has a customized notification. If so, those settings are used, otherwise the default notifications are used.\n\nUsing this functionality, you could set things up so only a few contacts show a popup while the rest trigger a regular notification. You could also ignore certain contacts by setting their notification to silent.

SMS Popup oferece a capacidade de personalizar notificaes em uma base por contato. Quando uma nova mensagem chega, SMS Popup ir primeiramente verificar se o contato possui uma notificao personalizada. Caso possua, essas configuraes sero usadas, caso contrrio, as notificaes padro sero usadas.\n\nUtilizando essa funcionalidade, voc pode definir as coisas de modo de apenas alguns contatos mostrarem um pop-up, enquanto o resto desencadeam uma notificao regular. Voc tambm pode ignorar determinados contatos, definindo a sua notificao para o modo silencioso.
